    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has various scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It recently passed inspection, but the tires will likely need replacement within the next year. This is a solid choice for someone who needs a dependable car and doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor upcoming maintenance.",
      "price": 18000.0,
