    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine runs well and the transmission shifts as it should, the car does show its age with some visible cosmetic wear on the exterior and minor staining on the interior upholstery. There are a few small oil leaks typical for its mileage, and the suspension is beginning to feel a bit soft, but it remains safe and functional. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been maintained just enough to stay on the road, though it will likely need some minor repairs and TLC in the near future.",
      "price": 18500.0,
