    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and reliable performance. This model offers a refined driving experience, featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior finish. It represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver who values both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. We invite you to experience the balanced excellence of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34800.0,
